<h1 class="page-headline">Edit Settings</h1>

<div id="discoverable-container">
  <button><%= link_to "Discoverable ON", bar_path(@bar, bar: {update_discoverable: true}, :format => :js), id: "discoverable", remote: true, :method => :put %></button>
  <br>
  <p>By clicking <strong>Discoverable ON</strong>, you'll be making this bar accessible in patron search results.</p>
</div>

<section id="close-tabs-container">
  <p>By hitting "Close All Open Tabs", you'll be closing <strong>ALL ACTIVE TABS</strong>.</p>
  <p>If you aren't tired, wasted, and closed for the night, and this isn't what you'd like to do, don't.</p>
  <br>

  <button><%= link_to "Close All Open Tabs", bar_path(@bar, bar: {close_all: true}, data: :success, :format => :js), id: "close-all", remote: true, :method => :put %></button>

  <div id="open-tabs-link"><%= link_to "Or go back to open tabs", bar_tabs_path(@bar) %></div>
</section>
